1013
01:08:21,970 --> 01:08:23,399
- Ito ay medyo malinis, tama? - Oo.

1014
01:08:23,400 --> 01:08:25,340
Okay. Panoorin.

1015
01:08:27,210 --> 01:08:29,039
- Isa, dalawa, tatlo, apat, - Sus.

1016
01:08:29,040 --> 01:08:31,649
- lima, anim, pito, walo. - Hayaan akong subukan.

1017
01:08:31,650 --> 01:08:32,780
