01:16:32,930 --> 01:16:36,930
(Madame Aema)

1153
01:16:39,170 --> 01:16:40,170
Kaya ito...

1154
01:16:41,000 --> 01:16:43,940
Ito ay dapat na napakahalaga sa amin?

1155
01:16:44,470 --> 01:16:45,540
Syempre.

1156
01:16:45,840 --> 01:16:47,710
Magiging maganda ang ating mundo.

1157
01:16:49,010 --> 01:16:51,850
Tingnan mo. Hindi kami menor de edad. Ano ang malaking bagay kung makita natin ito?

1158
01:16:53,180 --> 01:16:55,750
Magmartsa na lang tayo doon nang nakataas ang ulo.

1159
01:16:57,020 --> 01:16:58,020
Tara na.

1160
01:17:02,490 --> 01:17:04,260
- Bumalik ka dito! - Hoy. Tumigil ka dyan!

1161
01:17:04,360 --> 01:17:05,360
I-freeze!

1162
01:17:05,560 --> 01:17:07,230
- Hoy! - Hoy. Bumalik ka dito!

1163
01:17:08,500 --> 01:17:09,500
Bumalik ka dito.

1164
01:17:09,600 --> 01:17:11,130
- Bumalik ka dito. - Hoy!

1165
01:17:14,170 --> 01:17:15,170
- Jong Hee. - Oo?

1166
01:17:15,171 --> 01:17:16,699
Tatakbo na lang ako papuntang banyo.

1167
01:17:16,700 --> 01:17:18,640
- Sige na. - Papasok na ako sa loob.

1168
01:17:19,740 --> 01:17:21,680
(Ang viewing area ay nasa kanan.)

1169
01:17:24,710 --> 01:17:25,710
Noon,

1170
01:17:26,750 --> 01:17:29,350
may uhaw sa loob namin na hindi namin kakayanin maliban kung tumakbo kami.

1171
01:17:30,380 --> 01:17:31,389
Darn it.

1172
01:17:31,390 --> 01:17:33,450
Kahit na hindi alam kung ano ang gusto namin,

1173
01:17:34,290 --> 01:17:36,260
ngunit hindi namin napigilan ang aming sarili.

1174
01:17:36,460 --> 01:17:38,290
Parang nagmamaneho na walang preno.

1175
01:17:55,640 --> 01:17:57,140
At sa dulo ng kalsadang iyon,

1176
01:17:58,380 --> 01:17:59,580
nakilala kita.

1177
01:18:08,090 --> 01:18:11,360
At diyan nagsimula ang kwentong ito.

1178
01:18:17,800 --> 01:18:20,630
(Isang Daang Alaala)

1179
01:18:39,350 --> 01:18:42,089
Kaya nakilala mo ba si Giant o hindi?

1180
01:18:42,090 --> 01:18:44,190
Kakalimutan ko na lahat ng tungkol kay Giant.

1181
01:18:44,590 --> 01:18:46,660
At sa halip ay mag-a-apply ako para doon.

1182
01:18:46,760 --> 01:18:48,759
Kumbaga, kailangan mo ng diploma para makasali sa Miss Korea pageant.

1183
01:18:48,760 --> 01:18:51,060
sus. Bumalik sa paaralan.

1184
01:18:52,800 --> 01:18:53,830
Paaralan.

1185
01:18:53,930 --> 01:18:56,669
Hey. Nagpaplano ako ng killer event.

1186
01:18:56,670 --> 01:18:58,510
Pumunta tayo sa isang 4-on-4 group date.

1187
01:18:58,710 --> 01:19:00,570
Isang group date? Kalimutan mo na.

1188
01:19:01,840 --> 01:19:03,639
- Ano? - Hindi ka ba medyo maliit na bagay?

1189
01:19:03,640 --> 01:19:04,950
- Huwag mo akong hawakan! - Ay naku.

1190
01:19:05,480 --> 01:19:06,580
Nagsimula na akong mag-diary lately.

1191
01:19:06,980 --> 01:19:08,680
"May ginawa kay Yeong Rye."

1192
01:19:08,880 --> 01:19:11,490
"It was fun. I was happy."

1193
01:19:12,120 --> 01:19:14,750
Ang mga salitang ganyan ay hindi talaga bahagi ng aking bokabularyo.

1194
01:19:14,960 --> 01:19:17,090
Ngunit salamat sa iyo, ang buhay ay naging mas masaya.

1195
01:19:17,490 --> 01:19:20,560
Manager, hindi ba pwedeng isang exception lang?

1196
01:19:23,930 --> 01:19:30,040
(6 na buwan ang nakalipas)
